multDistributesOverMinusLeft (S left) Z          right =
   (S left - Z) * right         ==< Refl >==
   S left * right               ==< sym (minusZeroRight _) >==
   S left * right  -  Z         ==< Refl >==
   S left * right  -  Z * right  QED
